<td style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em; font-weight:bold; border-top:1px solid #aaa; border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;"><a href="/wiki/File:Portal.svg" class="image" title="Portal.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Portal.svg/13px-Portal.svg.png" width="13" height="13" border="0" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Portal:Communism" title="Portal:Communism">Communism portal</a> <a href="/wiki/File:Hammer_and_sickle_transparent.svg" class="image" title="Hammer and sickle transparent.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b1/Hammer_and_sickle_transparent.svg/12px-Hammer_and_sickle_transparent.svg.png" width="12" height="12" border="0" /></a></td>
