<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFKarl2007"><strong class="selflink">Karl, Marx</strong> (2007). James Ledbetter. ed. <i>Dispatches for the New York Tribune: Selected Journalism of Karl Marx</i>. <a href="/wiki/Penguin_Books" title="Penguin Books">Penguin Books</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780141441924" class="internal">ISBN 9780141441924</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Dispatches+for+the+New+York+Tribune%3A+Selected+Journalism+of+Karl+Marx&amp;rft.aulast=Karl&amp;rft.aufirst=Marx&amp;rft.au=Karl%2C+Marx&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BPenguin+Books%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=9780141441924&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Karl_Marx"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
