<li><a href="http://www.cato.org/pubs/journal/cj11n3/cj11n3-6.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.cato.org/pubs/journal/cj11n3/cj11n3-6.pdf" rel="nofollow">Liberalism, Marxism and The State</a>, by Ralph Raico</li>
