<li><a href="http://www.emis.ams.org/journals/DMJDMV/xvol-icm/19/Dauben.MAN.html" class="external text" title="http://www.emis.ams.org/journals/DMJDMV/xvol-icm/19/Dauben.MAN.html" rel="nofollow">Marx, Mao and mathematics: the politics of infinitesimals</a>, by Joseph Dauben</li>
<li><a href="http://www.wsws.org/articles/2006/may2006/rock-m02.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.wsws.org/articles/2006/may2006/rock-m02.shtml" rel="nofollow">Hegel, Marx, Engels, and the Origins of Marxism</a>, by David North</li>
<li><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio4/history/inourtime/inourtime_20050714.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio4/history/inourtime/inourtime_20050714.shtml" rel="nofollow">BBC Radio 4 'In Our Time' programme on Marx</a></li>
