<th style=";" colspan="2" class="navbox-title">
<div style="float:left; width:6em;text-align:left;">
<div class="noprint plainlinksneverexpand navbar" style="background:none; padding:0; font-weight:normal;;;border:none;; font-size:xx-small;"><a href="/wiki/Template:Marx/Engels" title="Template:Marx/Engels"><span title="View this template" style=";;border:none;">v</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Marx/Engels" title="Template talk:Marx/Engels"><span title="Discussion about this template" style=";;border:none;">d</span></a>&#160;<span style="font-size:80%;">•</span>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Marx/Engels&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Marx/Engels&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow"><span title="Edit this template" style=";;border:none;;">e</span></a></div>
</div>
<span style="font-size:110%;">The works of <strong class="selflink">Karl Marx</strong> and <a href="/wiki/Friedrich_Engels" title="Friedrich Engels">Friedrich Engels</a></span></th>
