<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Marx</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><i><a href="/wiki/Critique_of_Hegel%27s_Philosophy_of_Right" title="Critique of Hegel's Philosophy of Right">Critique of Hegel's Philosophy of Right</a></i> (1843), <i><a href="/wiki/On_the_Jewish_Question" title="On the Jewish Question">On the Jewish Question</a></i> (1843), <i>Notes on James Mill</i> (1844), <i><a href="/wiki/Economic_and_Philosophical_Manuscripts_of_1844" title="Economic and Philosophical Manuscripts of 1844">Economic and Philosophical Manuscripts of 1844</a></i> (1844), <i><a href="/wiki/Theses_on_Feuerbach" title="Theses on Feuerbach">Theses on Feuerbach</a></i> (1845), <i><a href="/wiki/The_Poverty_of_Philosophy" title="The Poverty of Philosophy">The Poverty of Philosophy</a></i> (1847), <i><a href="/wiki/Wage-Labor_and_Capital" title="Wage-Labor and Capital">Wage-Labor and Capital</a></i> (1847), <i><a href="/wiki/The_Eighteenth_Brumaire_of_Louis_Napoleon" title="The Eighteenth Brumaire of Louis Napoleon">The Eighteenth Brumaire of Louis Napoleon</a></i> (1852), <i><a href="/wiki/Grundrisse" title="Grundrisse">Grundrisse</a></i> (1857), <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Preface_to_A_Contribution_to_the_Critique_of_Political_Economy&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Preface to A Contribution to the Critique of Political Economy (page does not exist)">Preface to A Contribution to the Critique of Political Economy</a></i> (1859), <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Theories_of_Surplus_Value&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Theories of Surplus Value (page does not exist)">Theories of Surplus Value</a></i>, 3 volumes (1862), <i>Value, Price and Profit</i> (1865), <i><a href="/wiki/Capital,_Volume_I" title="Capital, Volume I">Capital, Volume I (Das Kapital)</a></i> (1867), <i><a href="/wiki/The_Civil_War_in_France" title="The Civil War in France">The Civil War in France</a></i> (1871), <i><a href="/wiki/Critique_of_the_Gotha_Program" title="Critique of the Gotha Program">Critique of the Gotha Program</a></i> (1875), <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Notes_on_Wagner&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Notes on Wagner (page does not exist)">Notes on Wagner</a></i> (1880)</div>
